name: Genesis of Revontheus
description: (Color Custom) Heavens ripped open, cries of angels in despair. When time was not yet know, and when worlds yet to exist. Revontheus, the true Revontheus, before his fall to the abyss, created this being whos power was known to tame time…he gave this being to those who managed to persist, the deceitfully dark abyss…
